[grunts]

27
00:02:14,440 --> 00:02:15,840
[Huang Jing] That ball is dangerous.

28
00:02:15,919 --> 00:02:16,760
[whooshes]

29
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:17,720
Damn.

30
