has been finalized.

31
00:02:23,880 --> 00:02:24,760
[gasps]

32
00:02:24,840 --> 00:02:26,040
-But...
-And...

33
00:02:26,120 --> 00:02:27,480
that is our locker room.

34
00:02:28,120 --> 00:02:29,320
[Siyang] You shouldn't be here.

35
00:02:30,040 --> 00:02:31,000
You can go now.

36
00:02:31,520 --> 00:02:32,600
I'm sorry.

37
00:02:38,640 --> 00:02:41,520
[teacher] This question is
from the other day.

38
00:02:41,920 --> 00:02:43,280
You've all seen it, right?

39
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:46,840
I will check your answers.

40
00:02:47,240 --> 00:02:50,600
Those who fail
will have to stay after school.

41
00:02:53,720 --> 00:02:54,760
Lu Xia.

42
00:02:57,280 --> 00:02:58,600
Answer this question.

43
00:03:13,680 --> 00:03:17,920
The answer is, "One-third times
the cube root of X. Wake up."

44
00:03:22,880 --> 00:03:24,520
You know you should wake up?

45
00:03:25,680 --> 00:03:26,720
Stay after school.

46
00:03:33,360 --> 00:03:34,600
Lu Xia hasn't come out yet?

47
00:03:39,800 --> 00:03:42,560
Hi! Can I practice here?

48
00:03:42,640 --> 00:03:44,480
Okay, follow me.

49
00:03:44,720 --> 00:03:45,680
Come.

50
00:03:45,840 --> 00:03:48,080
STRUCK TEN BOTTLES

51
00:03:48,720 --> 00:03:50,360
[Xiuwen] Jing.
[chuckles softly]

52
00:03:51,560 --> 00:03:53,080
Are you here to practice?

53
00:03:53,880 --> 00:03:55,080
Why is he here again?

54
00:03:55,440 --> 00:03:59,720
You have to pass the test
to practice during non-practice time.

55
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:01,080
What kind of test?

56
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,400
[Huang Jing] The rule is simple.

57
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:07,640
-[gasps]
-If you can strike that can ten times,

58
00:04:07,720 --> 00:04:09,280
then you can get ten drinks.

59
00:04:10,040 --> 00:04:11,640
It's a good deal!

60
00:04:12,160 --> 00:04:14,320
Ying, you're lucky you were not
punished for helping him.

61
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,920
-Mm-hmm.
-I was so scared.

62
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,040
I didn't think that much.

63
00:04:17,160 --> 00:04:20,000
I wonder if he's still in the classroom.

64
00:04:20,079 --> 00:04:22,200
No way, he must be on the court now.

65
00:04:22,279 --> 00:04:23,800
Come. Let's watch him play.

66
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:28,080
[Xiuwen] Go! Go! Go!

67
00:04:30,160 --> 00:04:32,120
[Mu] Damn, I can't hit it.

68
00:04:32,200 --> 00:04:33,480
Just one more.

69
00:04:33,560 --> 00:04:35,560
It's okay. You can have ten more attempts.

70
00:04:35,640 --> 00:04:39,240
[Xiuwen] Go! Go! Go!

71
00:04:39,320 --> 00:04:40,320
Go...

72
00:04:41,760 --> 00:04:42,840
[sighs]

73
00:04:42,920 --> 00:04:45,000
[exhales sharply]
Almost there.

74
00:04:56,680 --> 00:04:58,760
I've drunk some of it. Will this do?

75
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:01,800
-Okay.
-[Huang Jing] Okay what?

76
00:05:02,040 --> 00:05:04,240
A rule is a rule.
You have to give us nine.

77
00:05:04,320 --> 00:05:05,720
Isn't it one drink for ten attempts?

78
00:05:05,800 --> 00:05:07,000
One drink for one attempt.

79
00:05:07,080 --> 00:05:08,360
It's a scam.

80
00:05:10,000 --> 00:05:11,440
Strike the can if you can.

81
00:05:11,520 --> 00:05:12,440
[clatters]

82
00:05:17,680 --> 00:05:18,600
[clangs]

83
00:05:19,280 --> 00:05:21,280
You again? Last time--

84
00:05:21,360 --> 00:05:22,600
You lost to him twice.

85
00:05:23,080 --> 00:05:25,440
Liar! There are stones inside the can!

86
00:05:26,760 --> 00:05:27,680
[clangs]

87
00:05:28,080 --> 00:05:29,280
You...

88
00:05:32,200 --> 00:05:33,720
[Mu] What a smash.

89
00:05:35,320 --> 00:05:37,040
If I hit it 100 times,

90
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:40,120
-will you give me 1,000 drinks?
-Kid.

91
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:42,200
How dare you strike my can?

92
00:05:42,280 --> 00:05:43,680
I taught you how to play last time.

93
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,080
Haven't you learned?

94
00:05:45,360 --> 00:05:46,200
What did you say?

95
00:05:46,520 --> 00:05:47,600
Do you want to be beaten up?

96
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,480
-[Huang Jing] You...
-[Mu] What are you doing?

97
00:05:49,560 --> 00:05:50,600
[clangs]

98
00:05:51,800 --> 00:05:52,840
[Qiao Chen] Whoa!

99
00:05:53,120 --> 00:05:54,360
I hit it on the first try.

100
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:57,640
We have such a good court.

101
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:59,520
You shouldn't fool around like this.

102
00:06:00,320 --> 00:06:01,240
Qiao Chen.

103
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,880
Senior.

104
00:06:07,400 --> 00:06:10,400
The freshmen are so passionate
about practicing.

105
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:13,160
You shouldn't bully them like this.

106
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,120
Yes.

107
00:06:15,280 --> 00:06:19,200
I'm just joking around with them.

108
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:22,480
[PA announcement] Huang Jing and Ma Xiuwen
from Class 7, Grade 11,

109
00:06:22,560 --> 00:06:23,920
come to the dean's office.

110
00:06:25,760 --> 00:06:26,920
Behave yourselves.

111
00:06:27,720 --> 00:06:31,200
[PA announcement] Huang Jing, Ma Xiuwen,
come to the dean's office now.

112
00:06:34,040 --> 00:06:34,960
[Qiao Chen] Wait.

113
00:06:38,360 --> 00:06:39,480
Who said you could leave?

114
00:06:40,000 --> 00:06:42,000
[tense music]

115
00:06:42,080 --> 00:06:43,280
[Ying panting]

116
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:45,600
[Qiao Chen] Lu Xia, the freshman, right?

117
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:49,280
-It's Lu Xia.
-What did I say? I know he's here.

118
00:06:51,680 --> 00:06:54,240
It was not fun to watch you play
with Huang Jing.

119
00:06:54,320 --> 00:06:56,480
-Let's have a game.
-Okay.

120
00:06:56,840 --> 00:06:59,760
Lu Xia, are you sure
you want to compete with him?

121
00:07:00,120 --> 00:07:02,000
Qiao Chen is a main player in Grade 11.

122
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:04,520
-Which side?
-Backside.

123
00:07:09,160 --> 00:07:11,560
Okay. Front side. You serve first.

124
00:07:11,640 --> 00:07:13,280
[Ying and Peng panting]

125
00:07:13,800 --> 00:07:17,240
Lu Xia can't beat Qiao Chen, can he?

126
00:07:17,880 --> 00:07:21,280
Why did you give up the serve?

127
00:07:22,360 --> 00:07:23,920
He can do the Twist Serve.

128
00:07:24,000 --> 00:07:25,520
Don't you want to see it?

129
00:07:28,160 --> 00:07:30,880
-Oh.
-What is the Twist Serve?

130
00:07:30,960 --> 00:07:31,800
Mm-mm.

131
00:07:41,480 --> 00:07:43,080
[thwacks]

132
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,080
[whooshes]

133
00:07:48,440 --> 00:07:49,400
[gasps]

134
00:07:49,960 --> 00:07:51,080
[both gasp]

135
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:53,960
Why so stingy?

136
00:07:54,560 --> 00:07:56,880
[Qiao Chen] Let me see
your legendary Twist Serve.

137
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:57,920
[snickers]

138
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:11,360
You are so arrogant.

139
00:08:14,640 --> 00:08:16,640
[thwacks, whooshes]

140
00:08:18,200 --> 00:08:19,440
[both gasp]

141
00:08:24,880 --> 00:08:25,960
[thuds]

142
00:08:29,320 --> 00:08:31,600
[Qiao Chen] I never thought the spin
could be that powerful.

143
00:08:32,240 --> 00:08:34,400
I can only hit the ball...

144
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:36,039
before it hits the ground.

145
00:08:39,360 --> 00:08:42,919
Lu Xia is awesome!

146
00:08:43,520 --> 00:08:45,520
[action music]

147
00:08:51,960 --> 00:08:53,520
[thwacks, whooshes]

148
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:58,960
[Qiao Chen] It still doesn't work?

149
00:09:02,520 --> 00:09:04,160
TWIST SERVE

150
00:09:10,320 --> 00:09:11,280
[panting]

151
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,240
Yes!

152
00:09:15,560 --> 00:09:19,040
Qiao Chen managed to return it
with brute force.

153
00:09:21,600 --> 00:09:22,960
[Qiao Chen] I can grasp the timing.

154
00:09:23,320 --> 00:09:25,120
Now I have to control my strength.

155
00:09:25,560 --> 00:09:27,760
How can I lose on strength?

156
00:09:30,120 --> 00:09:31,360
[grunts]

157
00:09:31,960 --> 00:09:33,080
[thwacks]

158
00:09:33,880 --> 00:09:34,960
[groans]

159
00:09:35,360 --> 00:09:36,560
[whooshes]

160
00:09:40,200 --> 00:09:41,160
[grunts]

161
00:09:41,640 --> 00:09:42,560
Qiao Chen.

162
00:09:43,160 --> 00:09:45,320
He seems to adjust to Lu Xia's serve.

163
00:09:45,960 --> 00:09:46,880
[Mu] Are you kidding?

164
00:09:46,960 --> 00:09:49,360
Did he manage to counter
Lu Xia's serve so soon?

165
00:09:51,480 --> 00:09:52,800
[Qiao Chen] He wants to do a lob.

166
00:10:04,920 --> 00:10:05,960
[grunts]

167
00:10:08,040 --> 00:10:09,080
[sighs]

168
00:10:09,160 --> 00:10:10,680
[gasping]

169
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:15,560
You fooled me with a drop shot.

170
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:21,880
[Qiao Chen] Again.

171
00:10:21,960 --> 00:10:23,520
He's not worried at all.

172
00:10:23,840 --> 00:10:24,920
[chuckles softly]

173
00:10:26,240 --> 00:10:29,440
Even when playing against a main player,
he still performs well.

174
00:10:30,160 --> 00:10:31,680
Lu Xia is awesome.

175
00:10:32,520 --> 00:10:34,120
-[chuckles]
-Mm-hmm.

176
00:10:39,800 --> 00:10:41,800
[tense music]

177
00:10:43,560 --> 00:10:45,120
[Qiao Chen] He changed to his left hand.

178
00:10:49,880 --> 00:10:53,160
[scoffs]
Fine. I give up.

179
00:10:56,120 --> 00:10:57,760
Why do you give up, senior?

180
00:10:58,240 --> 00:11:00,200
He didn't even use his dominant hand.

181
00:11:02,680 --> 00:11:04,120
[Mu] A left-hander?

182
00:11:07,480 --> 00:11:09,960
[Qiao Chen] Luckily, we won't play
against him in the qualifying.

183
00:11:14,320 --> 00:11:15,960
[Mu breathing heavily]

184
00:11:16,040 --> 00:11:18,720
Lu Xia, Huang Jing admitted his defeat
and gave us these.

185
00:11:20,040 --> 00:11:22,840
Kid, Yu Qing shouldn't be underestimated.

186
00:11:24,440 --> 00:11:25,480
[Lu Xia] Fine.

187
00:11:31,160 --> 00:11:32,200
Senior,

188
00:11:32,640 --> 00:11:34,680
you still have the bandage on your foot.

189
00:11:35,000 --> 00:11:36,760
The doctor said that it is almost healed.

190
00:11:36,840 --> 00:11:38,720
I just need a while to recover.

191
00:11:38,800 --> 00:11:39,680
But...

192
00:11:39,760 --> 00:11:42,360
It's okay. He's pretty good.

193
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:46,320
He already knew my injury.

194
00:11:46,400 --> 00:11:48,080
Did he know?

195
00:11:48,440 --> 00:11:49,640
[snickers]

196
00:11:54,680 --> 00:11:55,600
[sighs]

197
00:11:56,680 --> 00:11:58,680
[playful music]

198
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:07,120
[grumbling]

199
00:12:09,920 --> 00:12:12,200
[panting]

200
00:12:13,480 --> 00:12:14,360
[exhales sharply]

201
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:16,400
What a bad day!

202
00:12:16,960 --> 00:12:19,160
Shut up and do your work.

203
00:12:19,240 --> 00:12:22,080
[Huang Jing] We have three floors to go.
The dean is going to check on us.

204
00:12:23,200 --> 00:12:26,120
How can I make up
a 2,000-word self-criticism?

205
00:12:26,200 --> 00:12:28,920
We wrote one before. We have a template.

206
00:12:31,440 --> 00:12:34,360
But you paid your debt.

207
00:12:36,120 --> 00:12:37,080
What debt?

208
00:12:39,400 --> 00:12:41,920
One hit for ten drinks, right?

209
00:12:42,000 --> 00:12:44,040
That kid hit the can ten times.

210
00:12:44,560 --> 00:12:45,800
That's...

211
00:12:47,280 --> 00:12:48,440
one hundred bottles of drinks.

212
00:12:49,040 --> 00:12:50,080
How many?

213
00:12:50,160 --> 00:12:51,440
One hundred bottles.

214
00:12:52,280 --> 00:12:54,240
But I begged them for you...

215
00:12:54,760 --> 00:12:56,560
with a bargain of 90 bottles.

216
00:12:57,040 --> 00:12:58,480
-[Xiuwen chuckles softly]
-You...

217
00:13:00,720 --> 00:13:03,680
I used your card. Here you go.

218
00:13:04,520 --> 00:13:06,520
[comical music]

219
00:13:06,880 --> 00:13:07,880
Huh?

220
00:13:10,680 --> 00:13:12,160
[Dayong] One, two.

221
00:13:14,320 --> 00:13:15,480
One, two.

222
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:18,880
One, two.

223
00:13:20,360 --> 00:13:21,800
-One two.
-Xiuwen.

224
00:13:22,560 --> 00:13:23,560
Xiuwen.

225
00:13:23,760 --> 00:13:24,600
Huh?

226
00:13:24,880 --> 00:13:25,880
Get that ball for me.

227
00:13:26,840 --> 00:13:27,800
[Xiuwen] Fine.

228
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,320
[grunts]

229
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:32,840
[thwacks]

230
00:13:36,960 --> 00:13:38,240
[Xiuwen] A middle-aged woman?

231
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:39,880
[Dayong] One, two.

232
00:13:41,240 --> 00:13:42,560
One, two.

233
00:13:42,640 --> 00:13:43,880
[Siyang] Everyone, gather round.

234
00:13:46,720 --> 00:13:49,480
Huh? Coach, you are back.

235
00:13:50,760 --> 00:13:51,760
Coach?

236
00:13:51,840 --> 00:13:54,360
[Siyang] Let me introduce her.
This is our coach, Qi Na.

237
00:13:54,440 --> 00:13:57,040
To prepare for the National
Junior Tennis selection,

238
00:13:57,120 --> 00:14:00,120
she has returned
to coach us this semester.

239
00:14:00,200 --> 00:14:03,680
[Coach Qi] After being away for a year,
I'm happy to see

240
00:14:03,760 --> 00:14:05,600
so many familiar faces in our club.

241
00:14:05,680 --> 00:14:07,280
And we also have some newcomers.

242
00:14:07,520 --> 00:14:11,200
Anyway, our goal never changes.

243
00:14:11,760 --> 00:14:14,600
We aim to win the national championship.

244
00:14:15,520 --> 00:14:19,040
[Coach Qi] For you, studying comes first.

245
00:14:19,120 --> 00:14:22,760
Only the hardworking students
can enter the qualifying.

246
00:14:23,640 --> 00:14:26,800
You have to be good at schoolwork
and school tennis competitions.

247
00:14:27,280 --> 00:14:29,960
Then you may have a chance
to compete for honors

248
00:14:30,320 --> 00:14:31,440
for our school.

249
00:14:32,080 --> 00:14:34,200
-Do you have confidence?
-[all] Yes!

250
00:14:34,520 --> 00:14:37,040
The grouping details will be posted later.

251
00:14:37,640 --> 00:14:38,880
You can have a look then.

252
00:14:39,760 --> 00:14:40,880
Be prepared.

253
00:14:40,960 --> 00:14:42,000
[Siyang] Keep practicing.

254
00:14:42,960 --> 00:14:45,240
Huang Jing, come here.

255
00:14:48,040 --> 00:14:50,040
[comical music]

256
00:14:52,560 --> 00:14:55,040
You may not have been taught...

257
00:14:55,760 --> 00:14:58,080
what to do and what not to do.

258
00:14:58,640 --> 00:15:02,000
I'll take responsibility for that.

259
00:15:02,640 --> 00:15:04,200
-Yes, ma'am.
-All right.

260
00:15:04,280 --> 00:15:05,400
Sorry, ma'am.

261
00:15:09,240 --> 00:15:10,240
[Huang Jing sighs]

262
00:15:12,080 --> 00:15:14,400
[Huang Jing] This coach is so tough.

263
00:15:14,760 --> 00:15:16,520
How can I lead the team?

264
00:15:17,920 --> 00:15:20,120
[Xiuwen] The coach talked to you alone,

265
00:15:20,200 --> 00:15:21,560
which means she values you.

266
00:15:21,640 --> 00:15:24,600
Many heroes in movies
have such experiences, right?

267
00:15:25,880 --> 00:15:26,880
LU XIA
YAN ZHIMING

268
00:15:27,320 --> 00:15:30,960
-[indistinct chatter]
-Hey. Look, they posted the list.

269
00:15:32,200 --> 00:15:34,720
What's good about seeing
the same names as before?

270
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:36,280
It's Lu Xia.

271
00:15:36,480 --> 00:15:38,440
[Mu] Lu Xia is in the qualifying.
[chuckles softly]

