00:30:56,080 --> 00:30:57,680
-[grunting]
-[Yan Zhiming] Bend his knees.

543
00:30:57,760 --> 00:30:59,080
Prepare to hit.

544
00:30:59,160 --> 00:31:03,080
So his physical exhaustion
is three times more than usual.

545
00:31:03,640 --> 00:31:05,520
So, it's a trial of physical strength?

546
00:31:06,800 --> 00:31:08,800
[Baiyang] Am I the one who's worn out?

547
00:31:08,880 --> 00:31:10,840
I am coiled by a "snake."

548
00:31:11,560 --> 00:31:14,040
[umpire] Lu Xia wins, 6-5.

549
00:31:19,320 --> 00:31:21,240
That kid showed me the wrong way?

550
00:31:22,960 --> 00:31:23,800
[grunts]

551
00:31:24,960 --> 00:31:25,920
-[thwacks]
-[groans]

552
00:31:26,320 --> 00:31:27,600
[Baiyang] It's getting hotter.

553
00:31:29,520 --> 00:31:30,560
[grunts]

554
00:31:31,160 --> 00:31:32,680
[panting]

555
00:31:34,200 --> 00:31:36,320
[breathing heavily]

556
00:31:36,640 --> 00:31:37,880
Damn.

557
00:31:40,080 --> 00:31:43,520
They are both exhausted.
But here's the difference.

558
00:31:43,920 --> 00:31:46,920
One already saw through his opponent,

559
00:31:47,000 --> 00:31:52,000
the other is worried
since his strategy didn't pay off.

560
00:31:52,800 --> 00:31:55,840
[Siyang] So their mental states
are totally different.

561
00:31:56,280 --> 00:31:57,280
I blew it.

562
00:31:57,960 --> 00:31:59,000
Baiyang.

563
00:32:02,640 --> 00:32:04,040
[Baiyang] You can't wait anymore.

564
00:32:06,600 --> 00:32:08,320
-[grunts]
-[thwacks]

565
00:32:08,400 --> 00:32:09,360
[grunts]

566
00:32:09,440 --> 00:32:10,320
[thwacks]

567
00:32:10,400 --> 00:32:11,280
[grunts]

568
00:32:15,680 --> 00:32:17,240
[Baiyang] I'm a little tired.

569
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:20,200
But you are, too.

570
00:32:20,560 --> 00:32:21,440
No one...

571
00:32:22,280 --> 00:32:24,120
can beat me with willpower.

572
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:27,080
[thwacks]

573
00:32:28,440 --> 00:32:30,600
-This...
-A buggy whip shot.

574
00:32:31,400 --> 00:32:35,320
A large range of motion from the bottom
makes the ball spin fast.

575
00:32:35,400 --> 00:32:37,760
The centrifugal force
makes the ball spin back.

576
00:32:38,320 --> 00:32:42,240
Many players around the world
take this as a weapon.

577
00:32:43,320 --> 00:32:44,720
Are you Miss Qi?

578
00:32:45,800 --> 00:32:47,600
I'm Qi Na. Nice to meet you.

579
00:32:48,120 --> 00:32:50,240
Miss Qi, I am a reporter
from Monthly Tennis.

580
00:32:50,320 --> 00:32:52,960
You can call me Sha.
We talked on the phone before.

581
00:32:53,440 --> 00:32:54,720
Just call me Coach Qi.

582
00:32:55,160 --> 00:32:56,600
Oh. Okay, Coach.

583
00:32:56,840 --> 00:33:00,800
I will report on the National High School
Tennis Competition.

584
00:33:01,080 --> 00:33:03,480
Uh, could you prepare
some materials for me?

585
00:33:03,560 --> 00:33:04,600
What materials?

586
00:33:05,040 --> 00:33:07,120
Some information on your main players.

587
00:33:07,200 --> 00:33:09,720
Such as height, blood type,
family background,

588
00:33:09,800 --> 00:33:11,200
and how they grew up.

589
00:33:12,280 --> 00:33:15,400
Why don't you report
on the development of junior tennis?

590
00:33:17,200 --> 00:33:19,880
Sorry, I don't know about that.

591
00:33:20,640 --> 00:33:26,400
I want to know their experiences
with this information.

592
00:33:27,360 --> 00:33:30,240
I want to start with him.

593
00:33:30,320 --> 00:33:31,280
[grunts]

594
00:33:32,520 --> 00:33:33,360
-[thwacks]
-[groans]

595
00:33:38,160 --> 00:33:39,440
[whooshes]

596
00:33:42,880 --> 00:33:43,800
[Qiao Chen] Really?

597
00:33:45,000 --> 00:33:49,040
[Mu] Lu Xia can also do a Snake-ball.

598
00:33:50,560 --> 00:33:51,560
What is this?

599
00:33:53,000 --> 00:33:55,440
This one is neck and neck with Baiyang's.

600
00:33:55,520 --> 00:34:01,520
[both] Lu Xia will win!

601
00:34:02,400 --> 00:34:03,440
Lu Xia.

602
00:34:03,840 --> 00:34:05,200
Oh. It's him.

603
00:34:05,760 --> 00:34:06,760
What's up?

604
00:34:06,840 --> 00:34:10,760
The way he plays tennis looks familiar.
I saw it somewhere.

605
00:34:11,159 --> 00:34:12,239
But I can't remember.

606
00:34:13,199 --> 00:34:16,120
The information on our players
is confidential.

607
00:34:16,199 --> 00:34:17,120
I can't reveal it.

608
00:34:17,480 --> 00:34:21,199
But you are a reporter,
it's okay if you can...

609
00:34:22,199 --> 00:34:23,440
discover it yourself.

610
00:34:24,480 --> 00:34:26,080
Uh, thank you, Coach.

611
00:34:29,760 --> 00:34:30,719
[sighs]

612
00:34:34,800 --> 00:34:37,840
[Sha] He plays like...

613
00:34:38,320 --> 00:34:40,800
Lu Xiangqian.

614
00:34:40,960 --> 00:34:43,000
-[Peng and Ying] Lu Xia will win!
-[Lu Xia] Surprised?

615
00:34:43,080 --> 00:34:45,400
-[Peng and Ying] Lu Xia will win!
-[Baiyang] How could it be?

616
00:34:45,480 --> 00:34:47,840
-[Peng and Ying] Lu Xia will win!
-This one is hard.

617
00:34:48,360 --> 00:34:50,239
I read it in a magazine.

618
00:34:50,719 --> 00:34:52,679
[Lu Xia] After seeing you do it,
I had to try it.

619
00:34:53,440 --> 00:34:54,800
It's really tough...

620
00:34:55,239 --> 00:34:56,639
since I don't have such long limbs.

621
00:34:57,440 --> 00:34:58,480
[Baiyang] The kid.

622
00:34:58,840 --> 00:34:59,920
How...

623
00:35:00,320 --> 00:35:03,040
It's beyond my expectations.
You can't master...

624
00:35:03,800 --> 00:35:05,520
such a trick within one day.

625
00:35:06,880 --> 00:35:07,920
Only a trick?

626
00:35:09,040 --> 00:35:10,440
There's one thing I've noticed.

627
00:35:10,880 --> 00:35:12,800
Lu Xia adjusted to the game quickly.

628
00:35:12,880 --> 00:35:15,640
[Yan Zhiming] He's pretty good.

629
00:35:19,960 --> 00:35:21,000
Senior.

630
00:35:22,320 --> 00:35:23,400
[clicks tongue]

631
00:35:24,880 --> 00:35:25,720
[chuckles]

632
00:35:25,800 --> 00:35:28,920
Hey, Baiyang.
It's like a nightmare, right?

633
00:35:30,280 --> 00:35:31,120
[sighs]

634
00:35:35,040 --> 00:35:37,320
[grunting]

635
00:35:40,400 --> 00:35:41,280
-[thwacks]
-[gasps]

636
00:35:43,560 --> 00:35:46,200
It's nothing serious.
He's always like this.

637
00:35:47,280 --> 00:35:49,280
[light music]

638
00:35:54,080 --> 00:35:55,600
What a pity, Baiyang.

639
00:35:56,160 --> 00:35:58,120
I'll never give up playing
as a main player.

640
00:36:00,200 --> 00:36:01,520
Never.

641
00:36:05,120 --> 00:36:07,160
Only you and Lu Xia

642
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:09,200
weren't defeated in Group D.

643
00:36:13,840 --> 00:36:15,080
I won't lose.

644
00:36:17,560 --> 00:36:19,560
[water sputtering]

645
00:36:25,680 --> 00:36:28,600
I can put on the uniform
once I become a main player.

646
00:36:29,200 --> 00:36:31,080
I worked hard for that.

647
00:36:32,200 --> 00:36:35,160
[Mu] Unfortunately, you'll play
against Yan from Grade 12.

648
00:36:35,800 --> 00:36:38,800
I think it's too difficult.

649
00:36:39,880 --> 00:36:41,600
Don't fool around, clean it.

650
00:36:42,360 --> 00:36:43,680
When did you start playing tennis?

651
00:36:46,120 --> 00:36:47,160
[Lu Xia] I can't remember.

652
00:36:48,200 --> 00:36:49,360
Have you ever lost?

653
00:36:50,240 --> 00:36:51,440
I lose every day.

654
00:36:52,600 --> 00:36:53,560
You must be kidding.

655
00:36:53,960 --> 00:36:55,120
[Mu] You are wonderful.

656
00:36:55,560 --> 00:36:58,880
You will be one of the top players
in the world.

657
00:36:58,960 --> 00:37:00,000
I'm not interested.

658
00:37:01,840 --> 00:37:02,760
Why?

659
00:37:05,120 --> 00:37:06,840
I just want to teach someone a lesson.

660
00:37:07,960 --> 00:37:09,560
Huh? Who?

661
00:37:13,520 --> 00:37:15,760
[Mu] Lu Xia, say it. Who is he?

662
00:37:15,840 --> 00:37:17,520
TENNIS CLUB QUALIFYING-GROUP B

663
00:37:20,240 --> 00:37:23,480
[Coach Qi] Lu Xia defeated Baiyang.
What a surprise.

664
00:37:23,560 --> 00:37:24,480
Yeah.

665
00:37:24,880 --> 00:37:26,200
Everyone is nervous.

666
00:37:26,520 --> 00:37:29,480
If we can keep it going
until the provincial competition,

667
00:37:29,840 --> 00:37:30,760
that is good.

668
00:37:31,640 --> 00:37:34,120
You seem to like Lu Xia.

669
00:37:35,280 --> 00:37:37,280
I still don't know what he is made of.

670
00:37:37,360 --> 00:37:41,040
I just let him play
with different players.

671
00:37:41,720 --> 00:37:42,680
[sighs]

672
00:37:43,800 --> 00:37:44,800
[exhales sharply]

673
00:37:44,880 --> 00:37:47,560
[Siyang] As a captain,
I have to know my players well.

674
00:37:50,400 --> 00:37:51,360
Auntie.

675
00:37:53,280 --> 00:37:54,200
Aunt...

676
00:37:54,520 --> 00:37:55,520
What?

677
00:37:55,920 --> 00:37:57,520
Uh, Coach.

678
00:37:58,440 --> 00:38:00,600
I can't find Lu Xia anywhere.

679
00:38:01,080 --> 00:38:02,360
[Ying] So...

680
00:38:02,440 --> 00:38:03,600
-So what?
-[Siyang sighs]

681
00:38:04,360 --> 00:38:08,160
I came to see if he's here.

682
00:38:08,240 --> 00:38:09,600
Do you care about him?

683
00:38:10,600 --> 00:38:14,160
No. I just want to congratulate him.

684
00:38:14,240 --> 00:38:15,160
[snickers]

685
00:38:15,920 --> 00:38:18,400
And you already knew about the list.

686
00:38:18,480 --> 00:38:20,520
Why didn't you tell me?

687
00:38:21,400 --> 00:38:23,040
So did Siyang.

688
00:38:24,960 --> 00:38:28,840
I think what I said was that
the list was finalized.

689
00:38:30,440 --> 00:38:33,360
I didn't know Lu Xia was in.

690
00:38:33,920 --> 00:38:35,560
We don't have practice today.

691
00:38:35,960 --> 00:38:36,800
But...

692
00:38:36,880 --> 00:38:38,000
What?

693
00:38:38,840 --> 00:38:42,640
He'll practice as well,
even if he has no opponent.

694
00:38:43,280 --> 00:38:45,320
Thanks, Auntie. Bye.

695
00:38:56,160 --> 00:38:58,320
Quick, he's here.

696
00:38:59,640 --> 00:39:01,640
[comical music]

697
00:39:01,920 --> 00:39:02,960
[Yan Zhiming] Ma'am.

698
00:39:04,520 --> 00:39:06,000
I would like 470 grams of celery.

699
00:39:06,080 --> 00:39:08,560
Picked before 5:00
