Are you looking for me?

712
00:40:27,880 --> 00:40:30,360
I heard that you were practicing here.

713
00:40:30,920 --> 00:40:33,720
I didn't want to disturb you,
so I just waited here.

714
00:40:33,800 --> 00:40:34,800
What's up?

715
00:40:36,200 --> 00:40:38,640
Congratulations,
you've defeated Baiyang today.

716
00:40:39,280 --> 00:40:42,680
Are you ready to play against Yan Zhiming?

717
00:40:43,280 --> 00:40:47,360
It is said that he knows everything
about every player.

718
00:40:47,840 --> 00:40:49,600
Playing tennis is not like doing math.

719
00:40:49,880 --> 00:40:52,080
Mm-hmm. Right.

720
00:40:53,320 --> 00:40:57,960
By the way, we formed a cheer squad
especially for you.

721
00:40:58,040 --> 00:41:00,920
