during the game.

722
00:41:02,760 --> 00:41:03,680
Fine.

723
00:41:05,120 --> 00:41:07,640
But I'll still try.

724
00:41:08,240 --> 00:41:10,160
Yu Qing can't lose
when it comes to sportsmanship.

725
00:41:10,240 --> 00:41:11,480
Thanks.

726
00:41:12,440 --> 00:41:14,240
Oh. Can I ask you something?

727
00:41:16,000 --> 00:41:17,000
Sure.

728
00:41:17,800 --> 00:41:19,840
Why do you play tennis?

729
00:41:20,400 --> 00:41:21,680
Because I have a goal.

730
00:41:22,880 --> 00:41:24,960
A goal?

731
00:41:28,520 --> 00:41:29,360
Yes.

